elements.name: As a Ghost user, I want to create a Posts

steps.name: I enter "<USERNAME>" into input field having css selector ".email.ember-text-field.gh-input.ember-view"
I enter "<PASSWORD>" into input field having css selector ".password.ember-text-field.gh-input.ember-view"
I click on element having css selector ".login.gh-btn.gh-btn-blue.gh-btn-block.gh-btn-icon.ember-view"
I click on element having css selector "a.gh-secondary-action.gh-nav-new-post.ember-view"
I click on element having css selector ".gh-editor-title.ember-text-area.gh-input.ember-view"
I enter "post de prueba" into input field having css selector ".gh-editor-title.ember-text-area.gh-input.ember-view"
I click on element having css selector "a.blue.link.fw4.flex.items-center.ember-view"
I should see text "post de prueba"
